                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for S Buisson &amp;lt;sbuisson@ddn.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/19614376-c5c2-11e7-9c63-52540065bddc&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/19614376-c5c2-11e7-9c63-52540065bddc&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The sub-test test_27 failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
